<abstract><t>This document specifies multipath extension for the QUIC protocol to enable the simultaneous usage of multiple paths for a single connection.  The extension is compliant with the single-path QUIC design.  The design principle is to support multipath by adding limited extension to [QUIC-TRANSPORT].</t></abstract>
